qMeasure.qLabel: Analyzer Capacity Minutes Used Last Month
qMeasure.qDef: Num(Sum({<[Access Type]={"Analyzer Capacity"}, last_month= {'1'}>} [Analyzer Capacity Used (Minutes)]),'#,##0')

qMetaDef.title: Analyzer Capacity Minutes Used Last Month
qMetaDef.description: Analyzer Capacity Minutes renew the first day of each month. This measure calculates Analyzer Capacity minutes used last month.
